\n- `Base64Converter.<clinit>(Base64Converter.java:52)`\n\nis the legacy fallback path:\n\n```java\nLoaderUtil.loadClass(\"javax.xml.bind.DatatypeConverter\")\n```\n\nThat branch only executes if the Java 8+ `java.util.Base64` path fails during static initialization. On the supported runtime for `log4j-core:2.17.1`, `java.util.Base64` is always available from `java.base`, so line 52 is not reachable through normal supported Log4j public API behavior.\n\nForcing that branch would require an unsupported runtime or artificial class-loading manipulation/shadowing of JDK classes, which would violate the task constraints. The existing added test remains the appropriate supported coverage path:\n\n- `tests/src/org.apache.logging.log4j/log4j-core/2.17.1/src/test/java/org_apache_logging_log4j/log4j_core/Base64ConverterTest.java`\n\nIt covers the supported `Base64:` byte-array conversion path and reached the Java `Base64` reflective initialization and decode call sites.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0655aa627cbc877a016a26056c25a88195b97ed47319e27300\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 27560, "output": 1782, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 29342, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1780876612874, "responseId": "resp_0655aa627cbc877a016a2605468a848195b436a291e1d1e097"}}
